<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero hero--subtle">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Support</span>
          <h1>Founders-led support throughout your Bhojan Mitra pilot</h1>
          <p>We sit in the trenches with our early partners. From the first discovery call to go-live and beyond, you’ll have real humans on call to keep service running smoothly.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Open a support conversation</a>
            <a href="#channels" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View support channels</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="channels" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Channels</span>
        <h2>Pick the support path that suits your team</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Founders hotline</h3>
            <p>Direct WhatsApp and phone escalation to the founding team during pilot weeks. We stay available through your peak hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Slack &amp; email support</h3>
            <p>Dedicated Slack connect workspace and priority email queue with same-day responses for configuration questions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Knowledge base</h3>
            <p>Step-by-step guides, FAQs, and troubleshooting checklists built from real pilot learnings. Updated weekly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>On-site visits</h3>
            <p>For multi-location partners we can schedule quarterly on-site audits to review setups and train new team members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ecosystem">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Response times</span>
        <div class="ecosystem-grid">
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Critical issues</h3>
            <p>Instant escalation via hotline. We jump on a call within minutes to resolve order flow or hardware blockers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card featured">
            <h3>Operational requests</h3>
            <p>Configuration changes, menu updates, or analytics tweaks handled within one business day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Feature feedback</h3>
            <p>We document every suggestion, share roadmap visibility, and schedule follow-ups when the feature ships.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need assistance right now?</h2>
        <p>Reach out and we’ll align on the best communication channel for your team.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact support</a>
          <a href="/training" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Plan a training session</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
